metadata.name: We Are Alone Together #266
metadata.description:
We meander through the flows of life, alone but together. This experience — an ultimately solitary one — is communicated but never truly shared. Our consciousnesses live in a perpetual separated state, alone but together.

metadata.name: Castles #82
metadata.description:
I made 1B pixel art for the first time and I had a lot of fun doing it. Generally the majority of my fxHash drawings were PFPs, which I wanted to change it as well. You can also use Castles as phone backgrounds. Oh also there is no rarity in it, every drawing has same weight.

For screen shot, open it Castles in new tab via fxHash button. And press("S") to take (1152x2048) screen shot.

metadata.name: Tower Rock #8
metadata.description:
Generative skies, land, sea, boats, birds, rocks, trees and more explode in this impression of the coast.  A day and night scene are randomly picked and painted using several of generative systems.  See if you can spot all the details!   

Press the Down Arrow to save a frame as a png.
